so to recap the features that i discovered


coulmn based filteration , filter the output based on specific conditon  in that coulmn

global filteration , using a search bar to filter the oytput based on a specific value , omits the need of makeing a state for each coumn(use fizzy filtering with ranking)

faceting , for coulmn filteration based on values of that column

sorting => sorts the output based on a specific coulmn


column visibility , pagination
